      "statement": "`plugin/settings.json` `\"agent\"` field sets the shipped plugin default main agent. Resolved: 2026-03-22. Outcome: `plugin/settings.json` sets the plugin's default main-thread agent for all users. Project `.claude/settings.json` can override this for local development (e.g., activating `harness:harness-orchestrator` explicitly). These are different configuration levels, not competing settings.",
